name: Swaptimize
description:
A re-implementation of Brain Warp, from the January 1983 issue of Creative Computing magazine.

This is a PROTOTYPE and I am gathering player opinions, both good and bad. Since this is not my original design, unfavorable feedback will not hurt my feelings :) 

In the comments, please rate this game on a scale of 1-10. Give one score for FUN and one score for REPLAYABILITY.
